<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:08:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>卡塔尔是加沙战争解决方案的一部分，而不是问题的一部分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/qatar-is-part-of-the-solution-to-gaza-war-not-the-problem/0000018e-f0c4-daad-a3de-fefff8c90000</link><description>美国议员发起的三起独立袭击事件似乎是协调一致的，他们指责卡塔尔在人质谈判和加沙临时停火方面缺乏进展。但这是一种明显不公平的评估，即使对本杰明·内塔尼亚胡来说这是一个方便的评估</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/qatar-is-part-of-the-solution-to-gaza-war-not-the-problem/0000018e-f0c4-daad-a3de-fefff8c90000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦摄影师在加沙拍摄的令人心酸的照片赢得了年度世界新闻照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/palestinian-photographer-wins-world-press-photo-of-the-year-with-poignant-shot-from-gaza/0000018e-f17d-d240-a19f-f57f28550000</link><description>路透社摄影师穆罕默德·塞勒姆 (Mohammed Salem) 凭借在汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 拍摄的失落场景获得年度世界新闻摄影奖，照片中 36 岁的伊纳斯·阿布·玛马尔 (Inas Abu Maamar) 抱着她五岁的侄女，她的侄女与她的母亲和妹妹一起被杀在以色列的一次袭击中</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:35:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/palestinian-photographer-wins-world-press-photo-of-the-year-with-poignant-shot-from-gaza/0000018e-f17d-d240-a19f-f57f28550000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室主任在总理审判中向国家证人提供带薪假期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-chief-offers-witness-in-pm-trial-paid-vacation-ahead-of-her-testimony/0000018e-f0ec-dc56-a9cf-f9ffc2310000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡曾试图罢免的总理办公室的一名法律顾问将在几周内就涉及滥用国家资金在内塔尼亚胡官邸提供餐饮服务的案件中作证。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:26:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-chief-offers-witness-in-pm-trial-paid-vacation-ahead-of-her-testimony/0000018e-f0ec-dc56-a9cf-f9ffc2310000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列来说，10 月 7 日是一场永远战争的开始。对于经济来说，这是否预示着永远的衰退？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/for-israel-october-7-marked-the-beginning-of-a-forever-war/0000018e-f10a-daad-a3de-ff3b6f320000</link><description>“全面胜利”是不可能的，战斗也没有结束的希望。但永久的战争将付出可怕的经济代价</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/for-israel-october-7-marked-the-beginning-of-a-forever-war/0000018e-f10a-daad-a3de-ff3b6f320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长正式要求联合国向加沙的以色列人质运送葡萄酒和无酵饼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/israel-minister-officially-asks-un-to-deliver-wine-matza-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018e-f0d9-d92e-abfe-f7ff5b9a0000</link><description>耶路撒冷事务部长梅厄·波鲁什在致联合国中东和平进程特别协调员的信中用希伯来语写道，除非获释，葡萄酒和无酵饼可以振奋以色列人质的精神</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/israel-minister-officially-asks-un-to-deliver-wine-matza-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018e-f0d9-d92e-abfe-f7ff5b9a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院将审理针对将警察局长隶属于本-格维尔的拟议法律的上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-hear-appeal-against-proposal-to-subordinate-police-chief-to-ben-gvir/0000018e-f0ad-de39-a79e-fbaf7f0a0000</link><description>以色列高等法院将听取针对国家安全部长提议的以色列警察条例修正案的请愿书，该修正案将允许极右翼部长制定战略并干预调查</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-hear-appeal-against-proposal-to-subordinate-police-chief-to-ben-gvir/0000018e-f0ad-de39-a79e-fbaf7f0a0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么当定居者杀害巴勒斯坦人时以色列人不退缩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/why-israelis-dont-flinch-when-settlers-kill-palestinians/0000018e-eca7-dd51-a79e-feb737eb0000</link><description>多年来，对巴勒斯坦人实施纵火、人身攻击甚至大屠杀的激进定居者被视为边缘极端分子，并受到广泛谴责。但随着一度边缘的私刑恐怖活动变得致命的例行公事，以色列人却未能做出回应</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/why-israelis-dont-flinch-when-settlers-kill-palestinians/0000018e-eca7-dd51-a79e-feb737eb0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日：哈马斯如何攻击以色列，一分钟一分钟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/what-happened-on-oct-7/0000018e-c1b7-dc93-adce-eff753020000</link><description>子子</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:41:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/what-happened-on-oct-7/0000018e-c1b7-dc93-adce-eff753020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击摧毁了加沙最大生育诊所的试管受精胚胎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-strike-destroyed-ivf-embryos-in-gazas-largest-fertility-clinic/0000018e-f084-dbb3-a3bf-f5cde45a0000</link><description>罢工摧毁了 4,000 多个胚胎以及 1,000 多个精子和未受精卵样本。加沙最大生育诊所创始人巴哈尔德丁·加拉伊尼 (Bahaaldeen Ghalayini) 表示，“我的心被分成了一百万块”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-strike-destroyed-ivf-embryos-in-gazas-largest-fertility-clinic/0000018e-f084-dbb3-a3bf-f5cde45a0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击后，战争结束的希望在加沙蔓延。很快就消散了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/hope-for-the-wars-end-spread-in-gaza-after-irans-attack-it-dissipated-quickly/0000018e-f033-d240-a19f-f43395680000</link><description>伊朗努塞拉特难民营的一名居民表示，加沙人希望国际社会对以色列施加压力，阻止地区大火，从而加大结束其在加沙行动的压力，但这似乎只会转移人们对加沙的注意力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 09:19:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/hope-for-the-wars-end-spread-in-gaza-after-irans-attack-it-dissipated-quickly/0000018e-f033-d240-a19f-f43395680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁表示没有义务向以色列国防军招募犹太学生或停止资助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-says-no-obligation-to-draft-yeshiva-students-to-idf-or-halt-their-funding/0000018e-f000-dbb3-a3bf-f5cd55cc0000</link><description>内阁的立场不利于司法部长，预计将在高等法院就此问题提出请愿书时要求一名独立律师。司法部长上周拒绝了这一请求，声称政府尚未就此事表明立场</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 07:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-says-no-obligation-to-draft-yeshiva-students-to-idf-or-halt-their-funding/0000018e-f000-dbb3-a3bf-f5cd55cc0000</guid></item><item><title>卫星图像显示伊朗弹道导弹袭击以色列空军基地造成的破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/satellite-image-shows-damage-from-iranian-ballistic-missile-strike-on-israeli-air-base/0000018e-ecba-daad-a3de-eebbd9190000</link><description>照片显示内瓦蒂姆空军基地 C-130 运输机附近滑行道受损，伊朗连夜袭击以色列，该基地遭到四枚弹道导弹袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 03:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/satellite-image-shows-damage-from-iranian-ballistic-missile-strike-on-israeli-air-base/0000018e-ecba-daad-a3de-eebbd9190000</guid></item><item><title>人身威胁和骚扰：伊朗升级针对以色列人的心理战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/personal-threats-and-harassment-iran-escalates-psychological-warfare-against-israel/0000018e-ecc8-dbb3-a3bf-fdcdb1840000</link><description>在政府数据库泄露重要信息、向以色列人质家属发送模拟葬礼花圈以及记者受到威胁后，数十名前公务员收到了来自海外的骚扰电话。 “这是伊朗持续不断的骚扰、制造混乱和分裂社会的行为。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/personal-threats-and-harassment-iran-escalates-psychological-warfare-against-israel/0000018e-ecc8-dbb3-a3bf-fdcdb1840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国高级官员将就拉法行动进行虚拟会面；伊朗威胁要“审查”核武器学说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-live/five-idf-reservists-in-serious-condition-following-rocket-drone-strike-on-northern-israel/0000018e-eecd-daad-a3de-eeff299e0000</link><description>伊朗指挥官警告德黑兰可能会在以色列威胁下审查“核学说” ■ 报告：以色列在逾越节之前不太可能对伊朗发动打击 ■ 美国对伊朗无人机计划、钢铁、汽车工业实施新制裁 ■ 哈马斯官员称人质交易/停止-火灾谈判尚未陷入僵局 ■ 联合国安理会将就巴勒斯坦加入联合国的请求进行投票</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-live/five-idf-reservists-in-serious-condition-following-rocket-drone-strike-on-northern-israel/0000018e-eecd-daad-a3de-eeff299e0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管缺乏安全经验，以色列内阁还是批准了本-格维尔任命的部主任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-rubber-stamps-ben-gvirs-pick-as-ministry-chief-despite-lack-of-security-experience/0000018e-ee06-dbb3-a3bf-ffcf41d40000</link><description>审查小组表示，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔的亲密伙伴拉斐尔·恩格尔“表现出了极大的学习动力”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 22:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-rubber-stamps-ben-gvirs-pick-as-ministry-chief-despite-lack-of-security-experience/0000018e-ee06-dbb3-a3bf-ffcf41d40000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处：以色列军队使用酷刑迫使工作人员承认与哈马斯的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-israeli-army-forced-staff-to-confess-ties-to-hamas-using-torture/0000018e-ed4f-d5d5-a59f-ef5f32280000</link><description>联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构发布的一份报告包括被以色列拘留的该机构工作人员的说法，称他们受到威胁和胁迫，承认该机构工作人员参与了 10 月 7 日的哈马斯袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-israeli-army-forced-staff-to-confess-ties-to-hamas-using-torture/0000018e-ed4f-d5d5-a59f-ef5f32280000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚大学校长成为美国反犹太主义战争的最新替罪羊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-17/ty-article/.highlight/columbia-universitys-president-is-the-latest-scapegoat-in-americas-antisemitism-wars/0000018e-ed1c-daad-a3de-ef3fff470000</link><description>这次听证会是自 10 月 7 日以来举行的第四次有关反犹太主义的听证会。但美国人仍然存在严重分歧，很难想象这些听证会如何能够促成合作努力，以平息大学校园中的煽动性言论</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:08:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-17/ty-article/.highlight/columbia-universitys-president-is-the-latest-scapegoat-in-americas-antisemitism-wars/0000018e-ed1c-daad-a3de-ef3fff470000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大航空 (Air Canada) 暂停飞往以色列的航班至 5 月底，加入易捷航空 (EasyJet) 行列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/air-canada-suspends-service-to-israel-to-end-of-may-joining-easyjet/0000018e-ed3e-daad-a3de-ef3f38d70000</link><description>加拿大国家航空公司在因加沙战争而中断六个月后，于两周前恢复了飞往以色列的航班。航空业官员担心，与伊朗的紧张局势升级可能会导致更多航空公司效仿其做法</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/air-canada-suspends-service-to-israel-to-end-of-may-joining-easyjet/0000018e-ed3e-daad-a3de-ef3f38d70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争，第 194 天：真主党在无人机和导弹袭击以色列北部的情况下造成至少 18 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-194-hezbollah-wounds-at-least-18-in-missile-attack-on-north-israel/0000018e-ed03-dbb3-a3bf-fdcf89fe0000</link><description>以色列北部真主党火箭弹袭击造成至少 18 人受伤 ■ 美国官员预计以色列将在伊朗领土上进行“有限打击”以回应伊朗袭击 ■ 英国外长：明确表示以色列打算对伊朗袭击作出回应 ■ 伊朗：军方已做好应对任何袭击的准备以色列对袭击“做出严厉回应” ■ 卡塔尔总理：停火谈判正处于“微妙阶段” ■ 战争已过去 194 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-194-hezbollah-wounds-at-least-18-in-missile-attack-on-north-israel/0000018e-ed03-dbb3-a3bf-fdcf89fe0000</guid></item><item><title>对于 10 月 7 日逃离哈马斯的以色列人来说，高速公路变成了死亡陷阱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israelis-fleeing-hamas-on-october-7-highways-turned-into-death-traps/0000018e-e196-d052-a78f-e5d690780000</link><description>因巴尔开车去打架，尽管他的女朋友恳求他不要这么做。莎妮设法与她的祖父进行了最后一次视频通话。他们只是加沙边境附近道路上无法躲避哈马斯的 250 多人中的两人</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:34:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israelis-fleeing-hamas-on-october-7-highways-turned-into-death-traps/0000018e-e196-d052-a78f-e5d690780000</guid></item></channel></rss>